snippet.title: Emptiness | First trailer
snippet.description:
In this amazing journey from emptiness to nowhere. With every step forward, new levels of emptiness unfold, expanding the boundaries of what seemed endless. Majestic landscapes, created by pixel art, gradually transform, offering players unexplored adventures and mysterious views.
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2761760/Emptiness/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/gent_fish
Music and sounds:
Alexandr Zhelanov - New epoch
Vitalezzz - subspace
